name: Shinobi of the Kathoonian Wisps
description: Hailing from the Dunes of Kathoon, the Shinobi of the Kathoonian Wisps are known to frequent Cinderkeep and consort with the mad wizard Zephyrial. Now finished uncovering the origin of the Clouddrop wisps, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
